---
import Icon from "../Icon.astro";
---

<section id="closing" class="build-closing">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="reveal build-closing__inner">
      <h2 class="build-closing__title">
        Don't see your <span class="build-cat__italic">shape</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="build-closing__body">
        If you have an operational problem and you're not sure what shape the
        answer takes, that's exactly the conversation worth having.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 15px; padding: 18px 28px;">
        Start a conversation <Icon name="arrow-right" size={14} />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
